<p class="text-[1.05rem] leading-8 text-foreground/88">If I cannot explain why a block exists, it probably should not be there.</p></div></div></article><section class="mx-auto grid w-full max-w-5xl gap-4 md:grid-cols-2"><div class="flex min-h-44 flex-col gap-4 rounded-[1.75rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/95 px-6 py-5 backdrop-blur-xl"><div class="space-y-2 border-b border-border/70 pb-4"><p class="text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.18em] text-muted-foreground uppercase">Previous post</p><h2 class="text-xl tracking-[-0.04em] text-foreground">No previous post</h2></div><p class="text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground">You are at the newest published entry.</p></div><div class="flex min-h-44 flex-col gap-4 rounded-[1.75rem] border border-border/80 bg-card/95 px-6 py-5 backdrop-blur-xl"><div class="space-y-2 border-b border-border/70 pb-4"><p class="text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.18em] text-muted-foreground uppercase">Next post</p><h2 class="text-xl tracking-[-0.04em] text-foreground">Designing Silent Interfaces</h2></div><p class="text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground">Notes on building interfaces that feel clear before they feel clever.</p><a class="mt-auto inline-flex w-fit items-center rounded-full border border-border/80 bg-card/90 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground transition-colors hover:border-accent/40 hover:text-accent" href="/blog/2026-03-29-designing-silent-interfaces">Open next</a></div></section></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--></div></div><script src="/_next/static/chunks/webpack.js?v=1775283033715" id="_R_" async=""></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"7:I[\"(app-pages-browser)/./node_modules/next/dist/next-devtools/userspace/app/segment-explorer-node.js\",[\"app-pages-internals\",\"static/chunks/app-pages-internals.js\"],\"SegmentViewNode\"]\n9:\"$Sreact.fragment\"\n1a:I[\"(app-pages-browser)/./components/site-navbar.tsx\",[\"app/layout\",\"static/chunks/app/layout.js\"],\"Sit